Uqinisekile ufuna ukususa le mephu? Ungayikhuphela kwakhona kamva xa kufuneka.
Le mephu ayinakususwa kuba yinxalenye yosetyenziso olusisiseko okanye iyafuneka kwezinye iimpawu. Iya kususwa xa ususa usetyenziso.
Akukho ziganeko zongezwe njengezintandokazi; qala ngokunqakraza uphawu lwenkwenkwezi kwisiganeko osithandayo!
Kubonakala ngathi i-GPS yakho icinyiwe, uyafuna ukuyivula?
Uyakwazi oku: ukuba ibali loMhlaba libaliswa kwincwadi enamaphepha ayi-1,000, uluntu luya kuvela kuphela kwisivakalisi sokugqibela sephepha lokugqibela.

Kodwa eli bali lifutshane linokuphela ngaphambi kokulindelekileyo. Sikodwa kwindalo iphela ebanzi nengenabomi. Sitshabalalisa yonke into. Sizicingela thina kuphela. Asinanceba. Sinobugovu. Simpumputhe. Kwaye sifuna ukongamela. Kodwa nathi sikwakwazi ukuvelana, sidala iimangaliso, siyomelela, sinokuzicingela abanye.
Kodwa asinaxesha lide. Senze inkqubela eninzi.. Singakha enye indlela: uluntu lwamalungelo, lobumbano, nwentando yesininzi. Kuxhomekeke kuthi!

Joyina intshukumo yehlabathi, uvuko oluxolileyo. Masenze amagagasi abantu, ubungqina bobuntu bethu bokwenene, umyalelo onamandla kubakhokeli bethu. Masihlanganisane kwiidolophu nakumazwe, kwihlabathi liphela. Masikhethe uxolo. Masikhethe uvuyo. Masikhethe indalo. Masikhethe THINA.
Kuthekani ukuba igagasi elinye linganele ukusidibanisa?

WorldWideWaves sisicelo sefowuni sexeshana esinenjongo enkulu: ukuququzelela uthotho lwamagagasi abantu adlula kwiidolophu ezinkulu, kumazwe. Kuza kwenzeka kwisithuba sonyaka omnye, le nyathelo lijolise ekudluliseni imida yomzimba nenkcubeko, likhuthaze umanyano, uluntu, namava esabelwana ngawo.
Entliziyweni yayo, i-WorldWideWaves ayisosicelo nje; yintshukumo yehlabathi eyilelwe ukudibanisa abantu kumboniso wobumbano nolonwabo, enamaxabiso esabelwana ngawo.
Ngokuxhoma kubuchwepheshe, i-WorldWideWaves iya kuvumela abathathi-nxaxheba abavela ehlabathini lonke ukuba bajoyine la magagasi abantu kwizixeko zabo, benze umbono onamandla nowuvusa iimvakalelo.

Ngamafutshane, i-WorldWideWaves yinzame enesibindi yokusebenzisa amandla obuchwepheshe ngesizathu esihle ngokwenene, ukudibanisa uluntu lomntu kumthendeleko womanyano, uvuyo nentshukumo edibeneyo. Nganye nganye igagasi, abathathi-nxaxheba abayi kunceda nje kumcimbi wehlabathi kodwa baya kuziva baze babelane nehlabathi ngefuthe elinzulu lokuhlangana njengeyona nto inye.
Wamkelekile kwi-WorldWideWaves! Siyavuya ukukubona ujoyina iziganeko zegagasi zehlabathi. Ukuqinisekisa ukhuseleko nokonwaba kwawo wonke umntu, nceda ulandele le miyalelo:

Inhlonipho kuWonke: Phatha bonke abathathi-nxaxheba ngentlonipho, kungakhathaliseki imvelaphi yabo. Nceda ugcine inhlonipho kubo bonke ababekhoyo; ukuziphatha okubandlululayo okanye ukuhlukumeza akuvumelekanga.
Hlonipha Izithuba Zikawonke-wonke: Gcina iindlela zivulekile, thobela imithetho neempawu zasekuhlaleni, kwaye ungavaleli iindlela zetrafikhi okanye ezongxamiseko.
Hlala Kwiindawo Ezimiselweyo: Ngenxa yokhuseleko lwakho, hlala ngaphakathi kwiindawo ezimiselwe isiganeko ukuba zikho.
Yiba noxanduva: Ukuba ukhetha ukusela, yenza oko ngobunono kwaye uhambisane nemithetho yasekuhlaleni.
Nciphisa Impembelelo Kwindalo: Lahla yonke inkunkuma kwizikhongozeli ezibekiwe uze ungahlwali ukuze iindawo zihlale zicocekile.
Xela Iinkxalabo: Ukuba ubona into engatshongo kakuhle okanye umntu okwingxaki, xela kwangoko kugunyaziso lwasekuhlaleni.
Nxiba Ngokufanelekileyo: Nxiba impahla nezihlangu ezitofotofo ezihambelana nemisebenzi yesiganeko kunye nemozulu.
Hlala Unamanzi: Zisa amanzi uze usele rhoqo, ingakumbi kwiziganeko ezifudumeleyo.
Qaphela Iimpahla Zakho: Gcina iimpahla zakho zikhuselekile uze uphephe ukuthwala izinto ezixabisekileyo ongazidingiyo.
Sebenzisa Inkqubo 'Yomhlobo': Hlala kunye nabahlobo okanye wenze abatsha, kwaye nijongane ukhuseleko lwenu omnye nomnye.
Lungiselela Iimeko Zongxamiseko: Gcina amanani ongxamiseko asekuhlaleni kwifowuni uze nivumelane nendawo yokuhlangana nabahlobo xa ningahlukana.

Hlala Uqaphile: Chonga iindlela ezikhuselekileyo zokuphuma kunye neendawo ezivulekileyo (umz., izikwere, iipaki) ezikufutshane, uze ulandele imiyalelo yogunyaziso lwasekuhlaleni xa kusenzeka ingxamiseko.
Amanani Ongxamiseko: Gcina inombolo yongxamiseko yendawo okuyo kunye neqhakamshelwano lakho lomntu ongxamiseko kwifowuni phambi kokuba ujoyine.
Xa Kusenzeka Ingxamiseko: Biza inombolo yongxamiseko yasekuhlaleni, phuma ngokuzolileyo uye kwindawo evulekileyo ekhuselekileyo, nceda abanye ukuba uyakwazi, uze ugcine iindlela zokungena zivulekile.

Ukukhululwa Kobutyala: Ukuthatha inxaxheba kwiziganeko ze-WorldWideWaves kukumngcipheko wakho. Ngokuthatha inxaxheba, uyavuma ukungabangi mabango kumenzi wesicelo ngokonzakala okunokwenzeka ngexesha lesiganeko.

Isaziso Sesithuba Sikawonke-wonke: Le yintlanganiso kawonke-wonke apho ukuthathwa kweefoto/ukurekhodwa kunokwenzeka ngababekhoyo okanye ziintatheli, ngokohambo lwemithetho yasekuhlaleni. Asibangi namalungelo kumfanekiso wakho kwaye asinakuwulawula umyalezo weqela lesithathu. Ukuba awufuni ukubonakala, zama ukuphepha iikhamera xa kunokwenzeka.
Kutheni kungekho msitho kwisixeko sam okanye kwilizwe lam?

Sikhethe amabini-khulu ezixeko ezinamaxesha amaninzi ehlabathini ukuze senze igagasi lehlabathi elinentsingiselo. Imida yezobugcisa neyokusebenza okwangoku ayisivumeli ukuxhasa iindawo ezingenamda. Sijolise kummeleli obanzi kwiilizwekazi, iinkcubeko neelwimi—into engenakugqwesa. Sinethemba lokongeza izixeko ezininzi ngokuhamba kwexesha.

Senze iiflegi zamazwekazi zokuqala, eziyimagqabhagqabha, ukunceda uchonge ngokukhawuleza izixeko kuluhlu nokubonisa umoya womanyano oxhaswa yi-WorldWideWaves. Ezi flegi azisesemthethweni kwaye zikho kuphela kule app; azijolise ukungcikiva okanye ukutshintsha naziphi na iisimboli zesizwe okanye zenkcubeko. Kuba akukho ziflegi ezisemthethweni zamazwekazi ehlabathi, senze ezethu ukuze kubekho ucaciso nenkxaxheba. Ukuba uyazithanda, zisebenzise ngokukhululekileyo.

I-WorldWideWaves yinzame yabucala ngokupheleleyo. Akukho nkampani, mbutho, okanye urhulumente ongemva kwayo. Abadali bafuna ukunikezela indlela eyakhayo kuluntu oluzibuza indlela abanokuphucula ngayo ihlabathi neemeko zobomi—umyalezo ozama ukudibanisa zonke iinzame ezikhoyo ezihambele phambili nezentando yesininzi phantsi komqondiso wexolo nongathathi cala kwezopolitiko.
Hayi. Usetyenziso lusimahla ngokupheleleyo. Nangona uyilo nophuhliso lwalufuna ixesha nemali kubadali, abangenelwa zimali buqu ngokuthe ngqo kulo.

Ewe, abavolontiya bamkelwa rhoqo. Ikhowudi yesicelo ivulekile (open-source) kwi GitHub, kwaye unokunxibelelana nabaqulunqi ku contact@worldwidewaves.net (iimpendulo aziqinisekiswanga). Eyona ndlela yokunceda kukusasaza igama: yabelana ngeefoto nevidiyo zeziganeko usebenzisa ii-hashtag ezicetyisiweyo, qhagamshelana nabachaphazeli basekhaya ukwandisa umyalezo, thetha ngale nto kuluntu lwakho, yaye okubaluleke kakhulu, joyina igagasi!
Ndingazifumana phi iindawo endinokuya kuzo ngexesha lezi ziganeko?
Ungafumana uluhlu lwezenzo ezicetywayo, imisebenzi, kunye neendawo apha: https://luma.com/worldwidewaves.

Cofa iqhosha elingezantsi ukuze uvule imowudi yokulinganisa. Kumakhusi esiganeko, sebenzisa iqhosha "play" ekhohlo phezulu komfanekiso wendawo ukuze uqale ukulinganisa kusetyenziswa iimpawu zesi siganeko (umhla, ixesha, indawo). Ukuyimisa, cofa iqhosha elifanayo. Ekugqibeleni, xa ugqibile, phuma kwimowudi yokulinganisa ngokucofa i-icon yokumisa kumaleko osisigxina.
Yiva isingqi seBig Apple ngoSuku loZimelelo, njengoko igagasi eliqaqambileyo lidlula eTimes Square, eCentral Park, nakumgca wesibhakabhaka omide wedolophu.
Vakalelwa bubuhle baseHollywood, imimoya yoLwandlekazi lwePasifiki, kunye nokuthandeka okuneenkwenkwezi kwe-L.A. ngexesha legagasi elikhanyisa iSixeko seZithunywa ngoSuku loZimelelo.
Hlonepha uSuku loZimelelo lwaseMexico entliziyweni ye-CDMX, apho umtsalane wekoloniyali udibana namandla anamhlanje, kwaye iingoma ze-mariachi zisithi ndindindi kwiiplaza zembali.
Vumela isingqi se-samba nomoya woSuku loZimelelo ukukusa ePaulista Avenue exakekileyo nakwimimandla ephilayo yale dolophu enkulu yehlabathi.
Bhiyozela uZimelelo lwaseArgentina phakathi kwezandi ze-tango, iibhulevadi ezinkulu zesimbo saseYurophu, nomoya onomdlandla wama-porteños ecaleni kweRío de la Plata.
Wonwabele iimvakalelo zeenkcubeko ezahlukeneyo zeNotting Hill Carnival njengoko eli gagasi lidanisa kwiindlela zembali, kwiibhasi eziphindwe kabini ezidumileyo, nakwiThames engapheliyo.
NgoSuku lweBastille, joyina igagasi elivela kwi-Eiffel Tower ukuya kwi-Champs-Élysées, libhiyozela uthando nobugcisa beCity of Light.
Yiva umoya womanyano ngoSuku loManyano lwaseJamani njengoko igagasi lidlula kwiBrandenburg Gate, kwiindonga ezigcwele i-graffiti, nakwoyilo lwale nkunzi iphuphuma bubomi.
NgoSuku lweSizwe laseSpain, vumela igagasi litshise iitapas bars zaseMadrid eziphilayo, iibhulevadi ezinkulu, nelifa lobugcisa lePrado.
NgeFerragosto, hamba kunye namaRoma neendwendwe kwiipiazza eziphila ngomculo, imithombo yamanzi, namandla eholide azalisa i-Eternal City phantsi kwelanga lasehlotyeni.
Ngomhla waseRashiya, mankanyela ubukhulu beRed Square neKremlin, njengoko igagasi lisithi ndindindi kwimbali yobukhosi esisityebi yesixeko kunye nengxolo yehlabathi yanamhlanje.
Bhiyozela uSuku lweRiphabhlikhi ngogagasi oluhamba ecaleni kweBosphorus, kwiimisikiti zemveli nakwiisikwere zale mihla, njengoko i-Istanbul ikhanya ngeeconcert, iiflegi, kunye neziqhumiso.
Bhiyozela i-Eid eCairo njengoko iindlela neemarike ziphila ngezibane zemibhiyozo, amavumba amnandi, neentsapho ezonwabileyo eziphawula ukuphela kweRamadan ngogagasi elidibanisayo.
NgoSuku lenkululeko, joyina igagasi ‘kwisiXeko segolide,’ apho izakhiwo eziphakamileyo zanamhlanje zidibana nelifa elityebileyo lokunyamezela nokwahlukahlukana kwenkcubeko.
Bhiyozela uSuku lweMadaraka phakathi kweemarike eziphilayo neendlela ezixakekileyo, apho ubomi besixeko budibana nesango ukuya kwizilwanyana zasendle ezimangalisayo zaseKenya.
Wamkela izingqi ezinamandla ze-Afrobeats ngoSuku loZimelelo lwaseNigeria, njengoko igagasi lidlula elona sixeko sixineneyo saseAfrika kunye neemarike zalo eziphilayo.
NgoSuku loZimelelo lwe-DR Congo, joyina igagasi elidlidlizayo kwisixeko esiphilayo ecaleni koMlambo iCongo, sizaliswe ngumculo nenkcubeko enedangatye.
Bhiyozela uSuku lweSizwe lwe-UAE ujikelezwe zizakhiwo eziphambili zekamva, imihlaba yentlango, kunye nobukhazikhazi besixeko sanamhlanje esikhokelayo ehlabathini.
Khumbula uZimelelo lwaseIndiya ngomoya weBollywood, izakhiwo zexesha lekoloniyali, kunye nonxweme olunethontsi lemvula ecaleni koLwandle lweArabia.
Yiva umoya wobuzwe ngoSuku loZimelelo njengoko igagasi lidlula kwiibhulevadi zexesha lekoloniyali, iinqaba zamaMughal, nentliziyo yekomkhulu laseIndiya.
Bhiyozela inkululeko kwiSilicon Valley yaseIndiya, apho iitempile zamakhulu eminyaka zidibana neepaki zobuchwepheshe bale mihla kunye nesixeko esixenene nesihlangeneyo.
Phawula uSuku loZimelelo lwaseIndonesia kwisixeko seentanganelo—ukusuka kwizakhiwo eziphakamileyo ezikhazimlayo ukuya kwiimarike zesitalato ezixakekileyo nakwiziqendu zelifa lenkcubeko.

Bhiyozela uSuku lukaTata weSizwe laseThailand lokuhlonipha uKumkani uBhumibol kwiSixeko seZithunywa, apho iitempile zegolide, iimarike ezidadayo, nokutya kwesitalato okuvuyisayo kuvuselela iimvakalelo.
Bhiyozela uSuku loZimelelo lasePhilippines kwisixeko apho ii-jeepney zidlula kwiicawe zeSpeyin zekoloniyali, kwiimarike eziphilayo, nakwizakhiwo eziphakamileyo zanamhlanje.
Joyina izigidi ecaleni koMlambo iSumida njengoko isibhakabhaka siqhuma ngemibala, kwaye umoya womnyhadala wasehlotyeni eTokyo udala iqonga elifanelekileyo logagasi elikhazimlayo.
Nandipha imibhiyozo ye-Gwangbokjeol njengoko igagasi lidlula kwizindlu zobukumkani, kwiindawo ze-K-pop, nakwisibhakabhaka esidibanisa isithethe nentshukumo entsha yanamhlanje.
NgoSuku lwaBasebenzi, khwela igagasi kwiipaki naseebhulevadi zaseBeijing, apho izigidi zihamba, zenze iipikiniki, zonwabele umoya weholide yaseNtwasahlobo.
Vumela igagasi liweqe iBund neNanjing Road njengoko iShanghai iphela zizintsapho, umculo, namandla ehlabathi ngomhla woSuku lwaBasebenzi.
Yiva igalelo leGolden Week yaseHong Kong, njengoko iVictoria Harbour, iimarike, neezitalato ze-neon zizala ngabantu ababhiyozela uSuku lwaBasebenzi kunye.
Khwela igagasi kwiMardi Gras Parade yaseSydney, apho iOxford Street igcwala imibala werainbow, iifolothi ezikhazimlayo, nomoya wekhanivali odibanisa amakhulu amawaka kwibhiyozelo.
NgoSuku lweMelbourne Cup, khwela igagasi kwisixeko senkcubeko njengoko isixeko sizala ngeparade, izihlwele eziphilayo zinxibe kakuhle, nomoya weholide 'wogqatso olumisa isizwe'.
NgoSuku laseCanada, ngxwelerha kulwandle olubomvu nolumhlophe njengoko igagasi lidlula i-CN Tower, iimimandla ezineenkcubeko ezahlukeneyo, nonxweme lweLake Ontario.
Bhiyozela uSuku laseCanada ecaleni koNxweme lwePasifiki, udlula kwiindawo ezimangalisayo 'ulwandle ukuya ezulwini', kubuhlaza beStanley Park, nakubuhle be-downtown.
NgoSuku loZimelelo, wonwabele i-deep-dish kunye nezimanga zoyilo ecaleni kweLake Michigan njengoko igagasi lihamba kwiWindy City.
Yiva umoya wenkululeko phantsi kobude obudumileyo beGolden Gate Bridge, njengoko eli gagasi loSuku loZimelelo lihamba ngeenduli, iinqwelo-ze, neemimandla ezahlukeneyo.
NgoSuku loZimelelo lwasePeru, dlula kwiiplaza zekoloniyali, kwiindawo zakudala zangaphambi kwama-Inca, nakumavumba anambithekayo ekhitshi lasePeru elidumileyo ehlabathini.
Bhiyozela uZimelelo lwaseColombia phakathi kobugcisa bezitalato, iimbono zeentaba, nomrhythm weendawo ezine-salsa kwikomkhulu laseAndes.
Yiva umoya wobuzwe ngoSuku loZimelelo laseChile njengoko igagasi lihamba ngasemva kwe-Andes, iifasadi zekoloniyali, kunye neenqaba zeglasi zale mihla.
Joyina iSizdah Bedar yaseTehran, usuku apho iintsapho zizalisa iipaki neegadi ngeepikiniki, uncumo, nentlaziyo, njengoko igagasi liwela ezi ndawo zangaphandle eziphilayo zesixeko.
Bhiyozela uSuku loZimelelo lasePakistan ecaleni koLwandle lweArabia, phakathi kweebhaza ezixakekileyo, imbali enotyebileyo, namandla ashukumisayo elona sixeko likhulu lesizwe.

Kufuneka sitshintshele kulawulo lomonakalo siye kukulungela izothuso. Amaqondo obushushu aza kudlula iinjongo esijolise kuzo, ngoko iiluntu zifuna isikhokelo esicacileyo, iziqheliso, nezixhobo ezilula ngoku.

Oku kuqala ngenyani esabelwana ngayo. Oorhulumente, iinkampani, nabakhokeli boluntu mababhengeze iinyani kunye, bavule idatha, bade bahambise iishedyuli ukuze isenzo sihambiswane, hayi sihlakazeke.
Ukukhusela ubomi, landelani ukwehliswa koxinzelelo ngeendlela zoxolo kwezo geopolitiki, nize nijolise kwakhona izibonelelo ekusindiseni abantu nasekuqinisekiseni uzinzo.
Buthanani kwelona nqanaba liphezulu norhulumente, amashishini, nabameli boluntu ukuze kubekwe izindululo etafileni, kunikwe abanoxanduva, kuza kuxelwe inkqubela.
Susahani izithintelo ngokugunyazisa iiprojekthi zovavanyo, nihambelaniswe imigangatho, nize nixhase kuqala ukomelela nokufikeleleka.

Phulaphulani abathathi-nxaxheba basekuhlaleni abajongene neempembelelo, nibeke iingozi ngokwamanqanaba kunye nabo, nize nishicilele izicwangciso ngolwimi olucacileyo nolulula ukuze uluntu luziswe ngolwazi kwaye lumenywe ukuba luthathe inxaxheba. Ukungasebenzisi ugonyamelo, ukubandakanywa, ukucaca, kunye nenzululwazi zikhokela lo mzamo.\n\nKwakhona zilungiselele ikamva: fundisani izakhono ezisebenzayo, tyalani kwiinkqubo zezilumkiso zangethuba, iziseko ezingundoqo ezinyamezelayo, nasezisombululweni ezisekelwe kwindalo, nize nakhe izixhobo ezivulekileyo nedatha yocwangciso loluntu.
Fumana izaziso xa amagagasi owathandayo eqala
